text: San Carlos Airport is an airport serving San Carlos, the capital of Cojedes state in Venezuela. It is also known as Aeropuerto Ezquiel Zamora. Runway length does not include a displaced threshold on Runway 15. ==See also== *Transport in Venezuela *List of airports in Venezuela ==References== ==External links== *OurAirports - San Carlos *OpenStreetMap - San Carlos *SkyVector - San Carlos Category:Airports in Venezuela Airport Category:Buildings and structures in Cojedes (state)
